swapETHForAllTokensAndMintExact(address,.details: Swaps ether for every underlying token in an index pool, then mints `poolAmountOut` pool tokens from the pool. Up to one intermediary token may be provided in `intermediaries` for each underlying token in the index pool. If a null address is provided as an intermediary, the input token will be swapped directly for the output token.

swapETHForTokensAndMintExact(address[],a.details: Swaps ether for each token in `path` through Uniswap, then mints `poolAmountOut` pool tokens from `indexPool`.

params.indexPool: Address of the index pool to mint tokens from.
params.path: Array of tokens to swap using the Uniswap router.
params.poolAmountOut: Amount of pool tokens that must be received to not revert.

swapExactETHForTokensAndMint(address[],a.details: Swaps ether for each token in `path` using their Uniswap pairs, then mints at least `minPoolAmountOut` pool tokens from `indexPool`.

params.indexPool: Address of the index pool to mint tokens from.
params.minPoolAmountOut: Amount of pool tokens that must be received to not revert.
params.path: Array of tokens to swap using the Uniswap router.

swapExactTokensForTokensAndMint(uint256,.details: Swaps a token for each other token in `path` using their Uniswap pairs, then mints at least `minPoolAmountOut` pool tokens from `indexPool`.

params.amountIn: Amount of the first token in `path` to swap.
params.indexPool: Address of the index pool to mint tokens from.
params.minPoolAmountOut: Amount of pool tokens that must be received to not revert.
params.path: Array of tokens to swap using the Uniswap router.

swapTokensForAllTokensAndMintExact(addre.details: Swaps an input token for every underlying token in an index pool, then mints `poolAmountOut` pool tokens from the pool. Up to one intermediary token may be provided in `intermediaries` for each underlying token in the index pool. If a null address is provided as an intermediary, the input token will be swapped directly for the output token.

swapTokensForTokensAndMintExact(uint256,.details: Swaps a token for each other token in `path` through Uniswap, then mints at least `poolAmountOut` pool tokens from `indexPool`.

params.amountInMax: Maximum amount of the first token in `path` to give.
params.indexPool: Address of the index pool to mint tokens from.
params.path: Array of tokens to swap using the Uniswap router.
params.poolAmountOut: Amount of pool tokens that must be received to not revert.
